snippet.title: Fire and Ice [Amiga Longplay] (1992) Graftgold
snippet.description:
Full playthrough of the Amiga game Fire and Ice. Released back in 1992 by Graftgold. A nice platform game with excellent graphics and music.

Full playthrough of the IBM-PC version of the game is available at https://youtu.be/CUm4kOy0w0w
